Title: An Act Changing the Name of Culaman Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Harden Joyce Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 744
An Act Changing the Name of Culaman Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Harden Joyce Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Culaman Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, shall be changed to Harden Joyce Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. The record of the Ministry of Education, Culture and Sports bearing the name of the school mentioned in Section 1 hereof shall be changed and be substituted by the name Harden Joyce Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 3. This Act shall take effect immediately upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
